  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0baa\u0b95\u0bcd\u0bb7\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sagara Kariyavasam will never abandon the people who have faith in the Rajapaksas",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is doubtful whether the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna-led government is currently in power.",
        "Podujana Peramuna General Secretary Sagara Kariyawasam said that it was the people made popular by the Rajapaksas who weakened the government and brought the entire country into crisis.",
        "He mentioned the above while attending a press conference held at the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna office (01) on Friday.",
        "The people of the country had complete faith in the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna Party.",
        "It was because of this belief that the people supported the political parties that joined us in the alliance.",
        "People who were popularized by the former Prime Minister Mahinda Rajapaksa have now unfortunately moved away from the government and are acting independently and have put the country in a complete crisis. Currently there is a government in the country.",
        "In the government led by United National Party leader Ranil Wickremesinghe, United People's Shakti and those who are independent from the government have got ministerial positions.",
        "The people of the country gave power to the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna. So we have responsibilities that cannot be handed over.",
        "The people of the country put their faith in the Rajapaksas and effected a coup, so it is my responsibility to protect the people's trust.",
        "Budujana Peramuna will never abandon the people who brought about the coup led by President Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "We are facing an economic crisis as a country. Various factors influence this. The economic crisis is not limited to Sri Lanka only.",
        "The people of the country should work together. All parties should give up narrow goals and act responsibly.",
        "The tourism service industry is declining day by day. Tourists will visit Sri Lanka only if there is a better environment, he said."
      ],
